        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h2>Features &amp; Benefits</h2>
            <p><span>1.</span>  <strong>TOP QUILT:</strong> The tight quilt combined with soft foam in the comfort layer help to give this mattress a medium feel. The top quilt features damask fabric quilted to .75-inch foam.  </p>
            <p><span>2.</span> <strong>COMFORT LAYERS:</strong> A 1.25-inch high-density convoluted foam topper and a blended cotton felt insulator pad offer a medium feel while also providing breathable comfort.  </p>
            <p><span>3.</span> <strong>SUPPORT SYSTEM: </strong>Our good-quality innerspring provides adult-level support and features a 312-count (full), five-turn, 13-gauge, knotted Bonnell coil and a 6-gauge border rod for edge-to-edge support and low-cost longevity.  </p>
            <img src="/Themes/OriginalMattressFactory/Content/images/product-features/Classic-Lux-Firm-Feature-Card_icons.jpg" class="img-responsive icons" alt="Classic Luxury Firm Mattress Icons" />
